metadata.name: S P O T L I G H T
metadata.description:
This surfer was kissed by the sunlight early morning.
I feel very connected to this shot as I find something really magic about it. This narrow, intense beam of light directly on this surfer and the ocean really resonate with me as it showcases what makes me happy

Date:
16.01.2022

Location:
Tamarama Beach
